Articles.Content: I can't get the better time warp UI to pop up, and I can't time warp more than before, what can I do to fix it? thanks!

Check that you have all the required dependencies.  I pulled my hair out for a bit getting a few of linux's mods to run.  Toolbar Controller is a dependency on several of them, but Toolbar Controller has it's own dependency in "Unblur".  Check the main page for TC and you'll see it listed there but not on the mods requiring TC.

Find Unblur here.
